"The Bones of What you Believe"

00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:34.530
helped propel Chvrches
to the top five

00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:38.400
of BBC'S Sound of 2013, an
award-winning appearance

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.424
at South by Southwest,
and a worldwide tour.

00:00:42.424 --> 00:00:43.965
Please join me in
welcoming Chvrches.

